SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4907
A bill to amend 2016 PA 407, entitled
"Skilled trades regulation act,"
by amending section 907 (MCL 339.5907), as amended by 2020 PA 89.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 907. (1) The Subject to subsection (3), the department,
2 in consultation with the board, shall promulgate rules for the safe
3 construction, installation, inspection, alteration, servicing,
4 operation, and repair of boilers in this state. For purposes of
5 this subsection, the department by rule may adopt or amend all or
6 any part of an existing published codification or national
7 standards and any amendments and interpretations of the
8 codification or standards.
9 (2) A departure from the requirements of this section is
